room_title: Escape room "Carat Capers" by Escape Games NM in Aztec
room_description: You are the son of America's most successful diamond merchants. As a child who spent countless hours at your parent's diamond shop, you picked up the art of lock picking. Over the last few years, you've cracked the safe at your high school... the supermarket... and the local gym. Today, you'll be facing your greatest challenge yet, as you and your friends decide to break into the most protected building in town.
